label: A7B_hP24_187_ah2j2kn_j-001
title: Cs$_{7}$O Structure
comments:
This structure is composed of Cs$_{11}$O$_{3}$ molecules, similar to the building blocks of the \href{current_web_home_dir/A11B3_mP56_14_11e_3e-001}{Cs$_{11}$O$_{3}$ structure}, interlaced with cesium atoms which have approximately the same spacing as in bcc-Cs. 
 Lattice constant data was given at $-150^{\circ}$C, while the atomic positions were given at $-175^{\circ}$C.
